From f732f1293b085d8cb1c603a67adc809d6370538d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 09:26:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Consolidate landing page modules: Trend Finder, Regime,
 Commodity Watch

Renames Bull Market Finder to Trend Finder (now featured/1st) and Regime
Shift Finder to Regime (2nd), per the repo's existing display-label-only
rename convention (routes/APIs/P-numbers untouched). Merges the Oil, Gold,
and BTC Tracker homepage cards into one tabbed Commodity Watch card (4th),
reusing each asset's existing preview component, route, and accent while
dropping the three redundant standalone cards. Earnings Beat Leaderboard
moves to 3rd. Updates Work.tsx traverse math/headline for four surfaces.
